      ## Commit message ##
    -    Add transport-smoke-suite orchestration foundation
    +    feat(smoke): add deterministic cross-transport smoke suite, claims, and matrix workflow
     
    -    Introduce a new workspace crate with shared env, claim, process, log, report, and scenario modules so deterministic smoke execution has a single auditable runtime contract.
    + ## .github/workflows/transport-smoke-capstone.yaml (new) ##
    +@@
    ++# ********************************************************************************
    ++#  Copyright (c) 2026 Contributors to the Eclipse Foundation
    ++#
